snippet.title: Project Relic Gameplay Trailer - Future Games Show GamesCom 2021
snippet.description: Check out this gameplay trailer from Project Relic, a brutal soulslike with big beasts and hectic combat. Keep your eyes peeled, as it's coming in early 2023.
